            Our team of medical experts consists of highly qualified professionals with extensive experience
            in their respective fields. We pride ourselves on delivering exceptional medical consultation
            services, ensuring personalized care for every patient.
          </p>
          <a href="/medConnect" class="connect-button">
            <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i> Connect with a Doctor
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
